{"id": "anc_sort_rows", "modality": "animations", "name": "Sort Rows", "task": {"description": "Create a self-contained 1920x1080 HTML animation (inline CSS/JS, NO <canvas>) of a small data table (a header row plus FIVE equal-height data rows, each with 3 cells). Over ~3s the rows re-sort by a numeric column: rows slide vertically to their new positions (a few reorderings). Rows keep equal height, aligned columns, and a fixed header.", "requirements": ["A fixed header row plus five equal-height data rows are present at every frame", "Data rows visibly change vertical order over time (re-sorting occurs)", "Rows never overlap each other during the reorder", "All rows stay fully within the viewport (none slides off the top or bottom edge)", "The three columns stay vertically aligned across all rows throughout", "By the final frame the rows are in sorted order with no overlap"], "difficulty": "hard"}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 23, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 2750, "rv_n_defects": 13, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 12640}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 50, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 2458, "rv_n_defects": 13, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 14244}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 66, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 3133, "rv_n_defects": 10, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 17227}], "ss_img": "images/animations/anc_sort_rows_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/animations/anc_sort_rows_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Animated Data Table Sort</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72 0%, #2a5298 100%);\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 16px;\n            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            padding: 40px;\n            width: 800px;\n        }\n\n        .title {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: #1e3c72;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            letter-spacing: -0.5px;\n        }\n\n        .table-container {\n            position: relative;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .table-header {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 10;\n        }\n\n        .header-cell {\n            padding: 20px 24px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-right: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .header-cell:last-child {\n            border-right: none;\n        }\n\n        .table-body {\n            position: relative;\n            background: white;\n        }\n\n        .data-row {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\n            height: 60px;\n            position: absolute;\n            width: 100%;\n            background: white;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\n            transition: transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);\n        }\n\n        .data-row:nth-child(even) {\n            background: #f9fafb;\n        }\n\n        .data-cell {\n            padding: 20px 24px;\n            font-size: 15px;\n            color: #374151;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            border-right: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\n        }\n\n        .data-cell:last-child {\n            border-right: none;\n        }\n\n        .data-cell.numeric {\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #059669;\n        }\n\n        .sort-indicator {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: -50px;\n            right: 0;\n            background: #f59e0b;\n            color: white;\n            padding: 8px 16px;\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            opacity: 0;\n            transform: translateY(10px);\n            animation: sortIndicator 3s ease-in-out;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes sortIndicator {\n            0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }\n            10% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n            90% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n            100% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); }\n        }\n\n        .table-body-container {\n            height: 300px;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h1 class=\"title\">Sales Performance Dashboard</h1>\n        \n        <div class=\"table-container\">\n            <div class=\"sort-indicator\">Sorting by Revenue \u2191</div>\n            \n            <div class=\"table-header\">\n                <div class=\"header-cell\">Sales Rep</div>\n                <div class=\"header-cell\">Region</div>\n                <div class=\"header-cell\">Revenue ($K)</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"table-body-container\">\n                <div class=\"table-body\" id=\"tableBody\">\n                    <div class=\"data-row\" data-revenue=\"245\" style=\"top: 0px;\">\n                        <div class=\"data-cell\">Sarah Chen</div>\n                        <div class=\"data-cell\">West Coast</div>\n                        <div class=\"data-cell numeric\">245</div>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"data-row\" data-revenue=\"189\" style=\"top: 60px;\">\n                        <div class=\"data-cell\">Mike Rodriguez</div>\n                        <div class=\"data-cell\">Southwest</div>\n                        <div class=\"data-cell numeric\">189</div>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"data-row\" data-revenue=\"312\" style=\"top: 120px;\">\n                        <div class=\"data-cell\">Emma Thompson</div>\n                        <div class=\"data-cell\">Northeast</div>\n                        <div class=\"data-cell numeric\">312</div>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"data-row\" data-revenue=\"156\" style=\"top: 180px;\">\n                        <div class=\"data-cell\">David Park</div>\n                        <div class=\"data-cell\">Midwest</div>\n                        <div class=\"data-cell numeric\">156</div>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"data-row\" data-revenue=\"278\" style=\"top: 240px;\">\n                        <div class=\"data-cell\">Lisa Johnson</div>\n                        <div class=\"data-cell\">Southeast</div>\n                        <div class=\"data-cell numeric\">278</div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        function sortTable() {\n            const tableBody = document.getElementById('tableBody');\n            const rows = Array.from(tableBody.children);\n            \n            // Sort rows by revenue (ascending)\n            rows.sort((a, b) => {\n                const revenueA = parseInt(a.getAttribute('data-revenue'));\n                const revenueB = parseInt(b.getAttribute('data-revenue'));\n                return revenueA - revenueB;\n            });\n            \n            // Animate rows to their new positions\n            rows.forEach((row, index) => {\n                const newTop = index * 60;\n                row.style.transform = `translateY(${newTop - parseInt(row.style.top)}px)`;\n                \n                // Update the actual top position after animation\n                setTimeout(() => {\n                    row.style.top = `${newTop}px`;\n                    row.style.transform = '';\n                }, 800);\n            });\n        }\n\n        // Start the sorting animation after a brief delay\n        setTimeout(() => {\n            sortTable();\n        }, 1000);\n\n        // Optional: Add a second sort after the first completes\n        setTimeout(() => {\n            // Sort by revenue descending this time\n            const tableBody = document.getElementById('tableBody');\n            const rows = Array.from(tableBody.children);\n            \n            rows.sort((a, b) => {\n                const revenueA = parseInt(a.getAttribute('data-revenue'));\n                const revenueB = parseInt(b.getAttribute('data-revenue'));\n                return revenueB - revenueA;\n            });\n            \n            rows.forEach((row, index) => {\n                const currentTop = parseInt(row.style.top);\n                const newTop = index * 60;\n                row.style.transform = `translateY(${newTop - currentTop}px)`;\n                \n                setTimeout(() => {\n                    row.style.top = `${newTop}px`;\n                    row.style.transform = '';\n                }, 800);\n            });\n        }, 3000);\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Animated Data Table Sort</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72 0%, #2a5298 100%);\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 16px;\n            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            padding: 40px;\n            width: 800px;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .title {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: #1e3c72;\n            margin-bottom: 60px;\n            letter-spacing: -0.5px;\n        }\n\n        .table-container {\n            position: relative;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .table-header {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 10;\n        }\n\n        .header-cell {\n            padding: 20px 24px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-right: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .header-cell:last-child {\n            border-right: none;\n        }\n\n        .table-body {\n            position: relative;\n            background: white;\n        }\n\n        .data-row {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\n            height: 60px;\n            position: absolute;\n            width: 100%;\n            background: white;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\n            transition: top 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);\n        }\n\n        .data-row:nth-child(even) {\n            background: #f9fafb;\n        }\n\n        .data-cell {\n            padding: 20px 24px;\n            font-size: 15px;\n            color: #374151;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            border-right: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\n        }\n\n        .data-cell:last-child {\n            border-right: none;\n        }\n\n        .data-cell.numeric {\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #059669;\n        }\n\n        .sort-indicator {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: -40px;\n            right: 0;\n            background: #f59e0b;\n            color: white;\n            padding: 8px 16px;\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            opacity: 0;\n            transform: translateY(10px);\n            animation: sortIndicator 3s ease-in-out;\n            z-index: 5;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes sortIndicator {\n            0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }\n            10% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n            90% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n            100% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); }\n        }\n\n        .table-body-container {\n            height: 300px;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h1 class=\"title\">Sales Performance Dashboard</h1>\n        \n        <div class=\"table-container\">\n            <div class=\"sort-indicator\">Sorting by Revenue \u2191</div>\n            \n            <div class=\"table-header\">\n                <div class=\"header-cell\">Sales Rep</div>\n                <div class=\"header-cell\">Region</div>\n                <div class=\"header-cell\">Revenue ($K)</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"table-body-container\">\n                <div class=\"table-body\" id=\"tableBody\">\n                    <div class=\"data-row\" data-revenue=\"245\" style=\"top: 0px;\">\n                        <div class=\"data-cell\">Sarah Chen</div>\n                        <div class=\"data-cell\">West Coast</div>\n                        <div class=\"data-cell numeric\">245</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"data-row\" data-revenue=\"189\" style=\"top: 60px;\">\n                        <div class=\"data-cell\">Mike Rodriguez</div>\n                        <div class=\"data-cell\">Southwest</div>\n                        <div class=\"data-cell numeric\">189</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"data-row\" data-revenue=\"312\" style=\"top: 120px;\">\n                        <div class=\"data-cell\">Emma Thompson</div>\n                        <div class=\"data-cell\">Northeast</div>\n                        <div class=\"data-cell numeric\">312</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"data-row\" data-revenue=\"156\" style=\"top: 180px;\">\n                        <div class=\"data-cell\">David Park</div>\n                        <div class=\"data-cell\">Midwest</div>\n                        <div class=\"data-cell numeric\">156</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"data-row\" data-revenue=\"278\" style=\"top: 240px;\">\n                        <div class=\"data-cell\">Lisa Johnson</div>\n                        <div class=\"data-cell\">Southeast</div>\n                        <div class=\"data-cell numeric\">278</div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        function sortTable() {\n            const tableBody = document.getElementById('tableBody');\n            const rows = Array.from(tableBody.children);\n            \n            // Sort rows by revenue (ascending)\n            rows.sort((a, b) => {\n                const revenueA = parseInt(a.getAttribute('data-revenue'));\n                const revenueB = parseInt(b.getAttribute('data-revenue'));\n                return revenueA - revenueB;\n            });\n            \n            // Animate rows to their new positions\n            rows.forEach((row, index) => {\n                const newTop = index * 60;\n                row.style.top = `${newTop}px`;\n            });\n        }\n\n        // Start the sorting animation after a brief delay\n        setTimeout(sortTable, 1000);\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>"}